name: Camp Alpine Express Dyneema Quickdraws (4 pack)
description: Light, strong and whippet thin, these quickdraws are designed for wandery pitches, alpine adventures and long multi-pitch climbs. The Photon wiregate carabiners are full-sized for easy handling while wearing gloves.Includes 2 lightweight full-size Photon Wire carabiners.Supple Dyneema® slings absorb less water than nylon, so they don't get heavy or iced-up on winter routes.Includes 4 quickdraws.
